title: Mobile County cattlemen celebrating beef at Gulf State Fair

Published By: Al.com: Mobile - Today 
The Mobile County Cattlemen's Association will be promoting beef Oct. 30 at the Greater Gulf State Fair in recognition of October Beef Month...
